{"tid":1130884,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"可能係連登第一個Dicord電台","createTime":"2019-04-29T10:34:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T02:15:54.000Z","uid":44132,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"efbe14f8559b0f46e1bcd393187683d9ffc6bfc4","tid":1130884,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T10:34:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">前言</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n最近發現Discord原來有個bot可以一路播歌 一路傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以想睇下有無巴絲打同我一樣無咩嘢做 又想搵嘢聽下 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁其他巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">節目時間表</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期一</span></span> [[[2300 - 0000 吹水]]] [[[0000 - 0115 駐台歌手]]]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期五</span></span> [[[2300 - 0000 吹水] [[[0000 - 0115 木人巷]]]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">星期日</span></span>[[[2300 - 0000 吹水]]] [[[0000 - 0130 感情台]]]<br />\n<br />\n詳情歡迎加入頻道後查詢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n而家已經有超過「<span style=\"color: gold;\">650<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"></span></span>」個巴絲打入咗頻道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲可以試下Call-In<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9UuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=dd4cd76c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「入咗台嘅巴絲打記住要開notification 方便追蹤本台最新消息」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9af52ce37b6ca59ee4b88e06ae96ba7ab3c921b3","tid":1130884,"uid":180499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc24a58083f1818ee96449d3dccf7d8df04c479","tid":1130884,"uid":44132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7ed56d8d501af5eeab6b07a5ae052b67c48c80b","tid":1130884,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:45:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01524a614d7a21be42b98b96979b9c9b412efb92","tid":1130884,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee468560abcf14376e0a8d31d1afc4dd49d06e7b","tid":1130884,"uid":229789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:57:21.000Z","msg":"help pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50b7fba57d055ae837a6c5220eae9378d249b37c","tid":1130884,"uid":126492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T14:58:30.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"985a9370482eb19244dda